<html lang="ca">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 — Pàgina no trobada | Red3Conecta</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cantarell:wght@400;700&family=PT+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="error-page">
      <div class="error-page__content">
        <span class="error-page__code">404</span>
        <h1>Aquesta pàgina no existeix</h1>
        <p>Pot ser que l'enllaç sigui incorrecte o que la pàgina s'hagi eliminat.</p>
        <a href="/" class="error-page__btn">Tornar a l'inici</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    font-family: "Cantarell", sans-serif;
    background-color: #F1E5D9;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .error-page {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .error-page__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .error-page__code {
    font-family: "PT Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FFB2A9;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: "PT Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6);
    max-width: 400px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .error-page__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .error-page__btn:hover {
    background-color: #FFB2A9;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>